Latias (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0379: Registeel
Pokémon
#0381: Latios →

Latias has been featured on 28 different cards since it debuted in the Theater Limited VS Pack of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Latias cards are normally Dragon-type or Psychic-type Basic Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Latias

Latias
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
